        "name": "In-vitro hemolysis data collection — FDA centrifugal pump, 2023",
        "description": "Prospective observational collection of hemolysis measurements from a recirculating in-vitro loop. Operating points were selected by engineering convenience to span the clinical operating envelope; no randomisation, blinding, or factorial experimental design was applied. Measurements at each operating point were taken in temporal sequence without washout periods between conditions. The protocol was reviewed by the device sponsor's biocompatibility team and deemed adequate for regulatory submission. Five operating points, triplicate sampling, ISO 10993-compliant circuit."
      },
      "metric": "Normalised Index of Hemolysis (NIH) g/100 L",
